'''Colin Udoh''' yin linlinwekantọ otò [[Naijilia]] tọn po tito televiziọn aihundida lanmẹyiya tọn bayitọ de po. Colin to azọn wa na Aihundida lanmẹyiya tọn Kwese tọn to alọnu din. E ko sọawuhia taidi studio analyst na Super Sport television network bo ko sọ kan linlin na African football magazine Kick Off he mẹlẹ yọnẹn ganji.
E sọ wazọn na Nigeria Football Federation taidi linlinnamẹtọ-gan dé. 
Udoh wlealọ hẹ yọnnu Naijilia-nu bọọlu-hotọ tògodo tọn dé he nọ yin Mercy Akide.







